        "description": {
          "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The sazakan surrounds itself in icy wind. Each creature within 10 feet of the sazakan must make a [[/save ability=strength dc=15]] saving throw. On a failure, a creature takes 28 ([[/damage 8d6 type=cold]]) damage, and is pushed up to 15 feet away from the sazakan and knocked &amp;Reference[condition=prone]. On a success, a creature takes half the damage and isn't pushed or knocked &amp;Reference[condition=prone]. If the saving throw fails by 5 or more, the creature is also &amp;Reference[condition=restrained] as its limbs become encased in ice. A creature, including the encased creature, can break the encased creature free by succeeding on a [[/save ability=strength dc=15]] check. The encased creature is also freed if it takes fire damage.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
